headline: Hormel Foods Corporation (HRL): A Bull Case Theory
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on Hormel Foods Corporation on X.com by @MoneyShow. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on HRL. Hormel Foods Corporation’s share was trading at $24.82 as of February 26th. HRL’s trailing and forward P/E were 18.00 and 15.90 respectively according to Yahoo Finance. Hormel Foods Corporation develops, processes, and distributes various meat, nuts, and other food products to foodservice, convenience store, and commercial customers in the United States
